<h3 id="start-with-what-youve-got">Start With What Youâ€™ve Got</h3>

<p>First step when resources are short?  Make the most of what youâ€™ve already got.  While in a perfect world Iâ€™d have access to the font on which the Capitals logo is based, in this case Iâ€™d have to make due with the letters (or rather, shapes) that make up the source logo I was starting with.</p>

